                                    para. 1 p. 1 lit. b DSGVO. We provide contractual services with "GoToWebinar". In
                                    addition to the implementation of webinars, this includes the follow-up of
                                    participation data for the creation of e.g. certificates of participation.
An order processing contract has been concluded with GoToWebinar on
